A web application that help folks create account and explore the beauty of Criador it provides.
Criador is useful to have your work items updated and helps you keep track of tasks that you create and want to bring into execution. It provides a bunch of features starting from having an account, to creating work items, setting the status/level of work done and motivates you to complete the work you started. 

The motive of this application is to help people track their works so that they can bring their idea to real world. It guides them by having a clean and sorted items to be performed. It even generate reports to analyze the amount of work done by an individual and also what is left to finish.

It reminds you of any work you have been inactive for quite a time and encourages to finish the job. 